== Correct translation of title of Krass article ==
Just wondering if the current translation of the German title ("''Das Gesicht, das den Kaiser auf die Palme brachte''") which is given as "The face that got the Kaiser's goat" is correct? Google translate gives me "The face that brought the emperor to the palm" instead. [[User:Anotherclown|Anotherclown]] ([[User talk:Anotherclown|talk]]) 21:28, 7 October 2016 (UTC)
